data.description: Just in time to bring the new year in with a new Beautiful brick ranch home.  Inside has a great layout with new floors in the living and family rooms.  Hardwood throughout most of the rest.  Kitchen boasts butcher block counter tops updated hardware and lighting throughout the home.   Partially finished basement with new carpet   New windows in 2015.   Awesome deck in the backyard that has your own creek.   Book your showing today!!!!  More Photos to come.
